WEBVTT

00:00:00.530 --> 00:00:02.291
TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT

00:00:02.291 --> 00:00:04.477
DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GODA.

00:00:04.992 --> 00:00:07.142
BELLA RABINOVICH.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.435
KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:13.105 --> 00:00:16.192
dertseylt itster vegn tog, vegn dem tog

00:00:16.192 --> 00:00:19.396
vi me hot aykh aroysgefirt fun Kovner geto keyn STUTTHOF.

00:00:19.210 --> 00:00:22.403
nu, zey hobn undz aroysge-, m'hot undz gefirt

00:00:22.403 --> 00:00:24.630
oyf, mit BATn azelkhene

00:00:24.630 --> 00:00:25.806
vu me firt...

00:00:25.034 --> 00:00:27.091
neyn, ober fun Kovne hot men aykh gef-

00:00:26.508 --> 00:00:30.297
nu fun Kovne hot men dos undz gefirt oyf az- mit azelkhene, mit a shif.

00:00:30.297 --> 00:00:32.928
in Kovner hafn hot men aykh arayngezetst oyf a sh-

00:00:31.929 --> 00:00:34.753
ye, m'hot undz gefirt oyf a shif

00:00:34.753 --> 00:00:39.297
oyfn vaser, un mir hobn gemeynt az me firt undz shoyn dertrinken.

00:00:39.297 --> 00:00:43.670
nu, zey hobn undz gefirt un gefirt, efsher a, mer oyf a (vokh) aza

00:00:43.157 --> 00:00:45.051
dos iz fun Kovne hot men aykh genumen firn.

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:48.437
ye, ye, hot men undz gefirt oyfn Nemen.

00:00:45.367 --> 00:00:46.174
durkhn NEMAN.

00:00:48.437 --> 00:00:50.543
mit azelkhene BATn

00:00:50.543 --> 00:00:52.771
hobn zey undz gefirt un gefirt

00:00:52.771 --> 00:00:56.227
iz nor geven mit mir mayn man un mayn bruder.

00:00:56.227 --> 00:00:58.771
fleg ikh alts zogn zey "(ot) firn undz dertrinken.

00:00:58.771 --> 00:01:02.613
ver es, ver es ken nit shvimen, ver s'vet zikh kenen rateven

00:01:02.613 --> 00:01:05.858
vet men zikh rateven." azoy hobn, flegn mir reydn tsvishn zikh.

00:01:05.858 --> 00:01:11.998
ober s'iz aroysgekumen az zey hobn nit gefirt dertrinken, nor zey hobn gebrakht tsu firn in STUTTHOF.

00:01:11.998 --> 00:01:16.279
zey hobn gebrakht tsu firn in STUTTHOF. velkher tog dos iz geven gedenk ikh nit.

00:01:16.279 --> 00:01:19.297
hot men undz gebrakht tsu firn in STUTTHOF

00:01:19.297 --> 00:01:22.630
azoy vi haynt gedenk ikh. UNK mir zaynen arayn in STUTTHOF

00:01:22.630 --> 00:01:24.577
oy vey mir nit

00:01:24.577 --> 00:01:29.367
kruves (shier) zaynen gelegn vu zey farbrenen mentshn. zogn mir "nu ot do

00:01:29.367 --> 00:01:33.472
z- do vet men undz shoyn rikhtik umbrengen; do veln mir shoyn nit lebn."

00:01:33.472 --> 00:01:35.438
ir zayt geven dernokh mitn man tsuzamen?

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.490
ye.

00:01:36.490 --> 00:01:38.595
mitn bruder un mitn man.

00:01:38.595 --> 00:01:44.157
zog ikh "do veln mir shoyn nit lebn; fun danet lebedike veln mir shoyn nit aroysgeyn; git a kuk vos do tut zikh."

00:01:44.157 --> 00:01:47.543
un, un mir zaynen arayn in geto, dortn in STUTTHOFF

00:01:47.543 --> 00:01:51.613
iz geven KREMATORIUMen vu zey flegn farbrenen di mentshn

00:01:51.613 --> 00:01:55.192
un zaynen geven mentshn, zogn zey "vos hot ir zikh gelozn do kumen; me-

00:01:55.192 --> 00:01:59.350
me, me kum- me kumt ot do um; me farbrent oder, zogn mir s'iz shoyn farfaln.

00:01:59.350 --> 00:02:02.209
vi z- vi got vet shoyn gebn azoy vet shoyn zayn."

00:02:02.209 --> 00:02:06.174
mir zaynen nokh geven in STUTTHOF a kurtse tsayt. dernokh iz aroys a prikaz,

00:02:06.174 --> 00:02:06.929
a bafel?

00:02:06.929 --> 00:02:10.484
a bafel az froyen bazunder un mener bazunder

00:02:10.484 --> 00:02:13.560
hobn mir tsugenumen dan mayn man un mayn bruder

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:15.753
un ikh bin shoyn geblibn eyner aleyn.

00:02:15.753 --> 00:02:20.315
un fun da- fun damolst on hob ikh im eyn mol gezen nor durkh di PROVOLKes

00:02:20.315 --> 00:02:21.980
durkh di dro- durkh di shtekhl

00:02:20.397 --> 00:02:22.894
ikh bin aro- du- du- durkh di shtekhl-drotn.

00:02:22.894 --> 00:02:28.368
ikh bin gegangen epes vos nit iz nemen; ikh gib a kuk: mayn man geyt, hob ikh ongehoybn shrayen

00:02:28.368 --> 00:02:31.999
un er hot ongehoybn loyfn tsum tsam un ikh tsum tsam

00:02:31.999 --> 00:02:34.719
un der daytsh hot oysgeshtekt dem

00:02:34.719 --> 00:02:38.526
dem biks un hot undz geheysn avekgeyn eyner fun dem andern, un mir zaynen avek.

00:02:38.526 --> 00:02:41.017
un dem bruder hot ir shoyn im UNK mer keyn mol nit.

00:02:40.452 --> 00:02:43.455
neyn, neyn. keyn mol nit. UNK keyn mol.

00:02:43.455 --> 00:02:48.525
un dem man nit.

00:02:48.525 --> 00:02:52.543
un, dertseylt a bisl vi s'iz, di ershte teg in STUTTHOF.

00:02:52.543 --> 00:02:54.631
nu vos, me hot gelitn hunger.

00:02:54.631 --> 00:02:56.718
keyn esn hot men dokh nit gegebn.

00:02:56.718 --> 00:02:59.560
zey flegn gebn esn, hobn zey gegebn azelkhene

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:03.490
groz, vos es flegt fun di groz onheybn vey ton di boykh.

00:03:03.490 --> 00:03:05.788
ikh hob oyfgegesn; ikh hob nit gevust.

00:03:05.788 --> 00:03:08.245
kh'hob gevelt esn; hob ikh oyfgegesn.

00:03:08.245 --> 00:03:14.104
iz er, ir zolt mir toyznter mol antshuldikn, hot mir gekhapt a PONOS, kh'hob gemeynt ikh kum um, ikh shtarb shoyn gor avek.

00:03:14.104 --> 00:03:19.771
ober fleg ikh shoyn mer nit nemen dos dem esn; ikh fleg nor nemen di shtikl broyt, mer keyn zakh nit.

00:03:19.771 --> 00:03:23.227
fun STUTTHOF fleg ikh in ergets nit loyfn un in ergets nit geyn.

00:03:23.227 --> 00:03:27.350
ir, ir gedenkt in vos far a barak zayt ir geven in STUTTHOF?

00:03:27.350 --> 00:03:33.648
in velkhn barak? epes shoyn links bin ikh geven; ikh gedenk nit genoy; nit ikh gedenk mayn NOMER, nit ikh gedenk dos.

00:03:33.648 --> 00:03:34.820
gedenk ikh keyn

00:03:34.315 --> 00:03:35.926
a NOMER hot ir gehat in STUTTHOF?

00:03:35.455 --> 00:03:38.384
nu to farshteyt zikh, un ikh gedenk nit, derharget mir.

00:03:38.384 --> 00:03:39.960
gedenk ikh nit dem NOMER.

00:03:39.314 --> 00:03:42.560
 vu vu, ver hot, ver hot aykh gegebn dem NOMER?

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:43.525
di daytshn.

00:03:43.525 --> 00:03:44.806
in vu, in STUTTHOF?

00:03:44.806 --> 00:03:46.560
in, in STUTTHOF.

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:48.139
(az m'iz) heftlinger.

00:03:48.139 --> 00:03:52.104
me flegt nor geyn mit di ge-, mit di late oyfn rukn.

00:03:52.104 --> 00:03:53.753
mit di late.

00:03:53.753 --> 00:03:59.128
ye, un ir, zayt in STUTTHOF hot i- zayt ir opge- in etsem STUTTHOF zayt ir geven a lange tsayt?

00:03:58.718 --> 00:04:01.413
ikh bin, nu kh'bin geven mistomen a dray khadoshim tsu

00:04:01.413 --> 00:04:05.858
fir khadoshim; dernokh hot men ongehoy- gefregt ver es vil forn oyf der arbet.

00:04:05.858 --> 00:04:10.419
hob ikh zikh glaykh farshribn tsu forn oyf der arbet, trakht ikh dos iz der eyntsiker

00:04:10.419 --> 00:04:14.568
di eyntsike veg vos m'vet efsher vi nit iz blaybn lebn.

00:04:14.568 --> 00:04:17.552
nu, un ikh bin UNK avekgeforn in lager MALKEN.

00:04:17.552 --> 00:04:20.398
in (KHINOV) iz dos geven der lager.

00:04:20.398 --> 00:04:22.833
un fun dortn hob ikh zikh bafrayt.

00:04:22.367 --> 00:04:24.647
ir dertseylt a bisl, ah

00:04:24.647 --> 00:04:26.647
 merer vi,

00:04:26.647 --> 00:04:29.437
vos iz, vi iz geven, vos hot ir geton in dem MALKEN?

00:04:29.437 --> 00:04:32.244
in MALKEN hob ikh ge- gearbet di OKOPes.

00:04:32.244 --> 00:04:33.592
vos iz dos di OKOPes?

00:04:33.393 --> 00:04:36.364
OKOPes, nu, grobn di erd, mit a lopete.

00:04:36.364 --> 00:04:37.700
un vos makhn?

00:04:37.603 --> 00:04:39.086
OKOPes far zey.

00:04:39.086 --> 00:04:40.834
dos iz shuts-griber azelkhene.

00:04:40.244 --> 00:04:43.981
ye, tsu b- zikh tsu bahaltn fun, fun a, fun a

00:04:43.981 --> 00:04:46.454
(hob ikh) ge- di gantse tsayt gearbet.

00:04:46.454 --> 00:04:48.463
un, vi

00:04:48.463 --> 00:04:51.366
der lager, vi hot zikh oysgezen der lager in MALKEN?

00:04:51.261 --> 00:04:54.594
der lager. der lager iz geven fun dikht gemakht.

00:04:54.594 --> 00:04:57.507
azelkhene barakes. in barakes zaynen mir geven.

00:04:57.478 --> 00:04:57.825
a-

00:04:57.507 --> 00:05:00.086
UNK shlofn oyf shtroy

00:05:00.086 --> 00:05:04.515
keyne betgevant, nit keyn elektrye, nit keyn zakhn, (alts) in der fintster.

00:05:04.515 --> 00:05:07.849
nit tsu fregn keyn mol zikh lozn arumvashn keyn zakhn

00:05:07.849 --> 00:05:12.647
ir zolt mikh toyznter mol antshuldikn, layz flegn geyn azoy vi kh'veys nit vos.

00:05:12.647 --> 00:05:14.927
m'hot genug oysgelitn, s'hot (geklekt)

00:05:14.927 --> 00:05:17.717
a sakh mentshn zayt ir geven in MALKEN?

00:05:17.717 --> 00:05:19.892
nu, a sakh.

00:05:19.892 --> 00:05:21.374
vifl umgefer veyst ir nisht?

00:05:21.261 --> 00:05:23.419
veys ikh nit, nor vos s'iz geven a sakh.

00:05:23.419 --> 00:05:25.619
velkhe mentshn zaynen dort geven? yidishe froyen?

00:05:25.173 --> 00:05:26.454
yidishe froyen.

00:05:26.454 --> 00:05:28.250
fun vanen zaynen zey geven merstn teyl?

00:05:27.770 --> 00:05:29.331
ale fun Lite kimat.

00:05:29.331 --> 00:05:30.500
kimat ale fun Lite.

00:05:30.243 --> 00:05:31.348
ale fun Lite.

00:05:31.348 --> 00:05:33.471
ober nisht nor ale fun Kovne.

00:05:33.471 --> 00:05:36.594
nu, farshidene. (i) fun Kovne, un nit fun Kovne.

00:05:36.594 --> 00:05:40.471
ikh'l aykh zogn: ikh fleg zikh azoy mit keynem iberiks nit farnemen, nor mit

00:05:40.471 --> 00:05:43.454
mit di mit nentste dortn, mit di nentste azelkhene.

00:05:43.454 --> 00:05:44.980
ver iz geven ayere nentste?

00:05:44.980 --> 00:05:50.910
di nentste? dos zaynen geven, nu, bakante, vos ikh hob zikh, zey gekent fun Kovne.

00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:52.171
ir gedenk zeyere nemen?

00:05:52.171 --> 00:05:55.401
ikh gedenk nit. derharget mir, ikh gedenk keyn zakh nit.

00:05:55.401 --> 00:06:01.264
ah, ober ir ged- ir gedenkt az, e- e- etlekhe froyen zaynen geven aykh nenter mit velkhe ne- UNK

00:06:00.278 --> 00:06:02.703
i- mit vemen ikh fleg zikh teyln, yo.

00:06:02.703 --> 00:06:07.394
v- vos, vifl barakes zaynen geven in algemeyn in MALKEN, gedenkt ir efsher?

00:06:07.313 --> 00:06:09.787
vifl barakes?

00:06:09.787 --> 00:06:13.278
zaynen geven mistomen a a tsvey-dray barakes.

00:06:13.278 --> 00:06:15.243
un vifl mentshn in eyn barak?

00:06:15.243 --> 00:06:16.892
ot dos gedenk ikh oykh nit.

00:06:16.892 --> 00:06:19.611
a sakh vayber. me flegt shlofn oyf di shtroy

00:06:19.611 --> 00:06:22.471
azoy vi, azoy vi

00:06:22.471 --> 00:06:26.260
vi khazeyrim. ir kent zikh forshteln.

00:06:26.260 --> 00:06:29.839
nit zikh tsutsudekn, nit keyn zakh nit. azoy hot men gelebt.

00:06:29.839 --> 00:06:32.155
un vos flegt men gebn esn in lager?

00:06:32.155 --> 00:06:33.576
in lager?

00:06:33.576 --> 00:06:36.436
dray hundert gram broyt un a bisinke zup.

00:06:36.436 --> 00:06:37.440
dos flegt men gebn?

00:06:37.190 --> 00:06:39.260
dos iz geven di ershte tsaytn.

00:06:39.260 --> 00:06:42.400
un dernokh tsum ende hobn zey dos shoyn oykh nit gehat.

00:06:42.400 --> 00:06:43.944
vos flegt men gebn dernokh?

00:06:43.944 --> 00:06:46.436
tsvey bulves mit a (kap) zup.

00:06:46.436 --> 00:06:50.357
dos iz geven di, un dos flegt men gebn ven, in der fri, mitogtsayt, in ovnt?

00:06:50.155 --> 00:06:55.480
in der fri, a mol farnakht, a mol in der fri, ven s- ven s'flegt zey arayngeyn in kop.

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:59.207
un esn flegt men gebn nor eyn mol a tog, tsu es hot pasirt az tsvey dray mol a tog?

00:06:59.207 --> 00:07:03.295
neyn, dray mol nit. me fleg gebn

00:07:03.295 --> 00:07:07.152
in der fri kave, un fleg di kave nit zayn mit vos tsu

00:07:07.152 --> 00:07:09.235
mit a shtikele broyt.

00:07:09.235 --> 00:07:12.663
un dernokh flegt men gebn di broyt mit a bisinke zup.

00:07:12.663 --> 00:07:14.541
dernokh, dos iz ven, mitogtsayt?

00:07:14.381 --> 00:07:15.519
ye.

00:07:15.519 --> 00:07:17.716
nor me flegt tsum kumen fun der arbet.

00:07:17.716 --> 00:07:22.295
un vos iz geven, vifl a zeyger flegt men aykh, ah, fun lager aroystraybn oyf der arbet?

00:07:22.295 --> 00:07:26.207
in lager? nu, zey flegn undz tsu, tsu,

00:07:26.207 --> 00:07:27.821
firn glaykh in der fri.

00:07:27.821 --> 00:07:30.170
un ir ge- ir gedenkt vifl UNK?

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:32.523
keyn zeyger flegn mir dokh nit hobn; mir hobn dokh keyn zakh nit gevust.

00:07:32.523 --> 00:07:35.821
zey hobn dokh altsding fun undz UNK fun undz tsugenumen. di zeygers

00:07:35.821 --> 00:07:38.207
m'hot alts vos m'hot getrogn, alts hobn zey tsugenumen.

00:07:38.101 --> 00:07:39.500
vu hot men dos tsugenumen?

00:07:39.410 --> 00:07:41.545
in, in, STUTTHOF

00:07:41.768 --> 00:07:43.333
in STUTTHOF hot men aykh tsugenumen.

00:07:43.125 --> 00:07:45.177
ye un in lager hot dokh keyn (mol) UNK

00:07:44.382 --> 00:07:45.856
ir hot gehat a zeyger bay zikh?

00:07:45.956 --> 00:07:46.888
kh'hob gehat.

00:07:46.821 --> 00:07:49.130
un in, in geto hot ir gehat bay zikh a zeyger?

00:07:48.748 --> 00:07:51.274
ye, kh'hob gehat alts.

00:07:51.274 --> 00:07:56.666
vi ikh hob in, STUTTHOF avekgeleygt goldene oyringlekh un a goldenem fingerl un a zeygerl.

00:07:56.757 --> 00:07:59.077
alts hob ikh gehat. far vos hob ikh nit gehat?

00:07:58.663 --> 00:08:00.923
iz in Kovner geto hot ir dokh alts oysgehit?

00:08:00.941 --> 00:08:03.205
in Kovner geto hob ikh dos oy- hot men dos oysgehit.

00:08:03.205 --> 00:08:05.166
mayne, mayn foter hot dos oysgehit.

00:08:05.506 --> 00:08:08.394
un dernokh UNK fleg ikh, hob ikh dos gegangen ongeton azoy vi

00:08:08.394 --> 00:08:10.663
in STUTTHOF hot men dos geheysn alts avekgebn.

00:08:10.768 --> 00:08:11.996
un dem zeyger oykhet?

00:08:12.107 --> 00:08:14.168
alts avekgegebn. alts avekgegebn.

00:08:14.168 --> 00:08:16.947
keyn zakh hob ikh nit gehat az ikh bin gekumen nokh di krig.

00:08:16.947 --> 00:08:20.435
itster vos ikh hob iz altsding fun mayne tsen finger.

00:08:20.557 --> 00:08:21.642
iz,

00:08:21.803 --> 00:08:23.856
itster, itster dertseylt

00:08:23.856 --> 00:08:26.540
der lager, der etsem lager in MALKEN

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:28.698
er iz geven bavakht mit shtekhl-drot?

00:08:28.746 --> 00:08:32.687
er iz nit geven bavakht mit keyn shtekhl-drot, not s'iz geven bavakht

00:08:32.687 --> 00:08:34.235
fun

00:08:34.235 --> 00:08:37.390
fun daytshn. zeyer a sakh daytshn flegn hitn dem lager.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:40.294
un er iz geven arumgetsamt?

00:08:40.277 --> 00:08:42.324
ye, dakht zikh. ikh gedenk shoyn nit.

00:08:42.324 --> 00:08:44.435
mir dakht zikh az ye, s'iz geven arumgetsamt.

00:08:44.435 --> 00:08:46.298
un alts eyns flegn zey undz hitn.

00:08:46.298 --> 00:08:48.470
vos heyst hitn?

00:08:48.470 --> 00:08:50.985
s'iz geven zeyer a groyse

00:08:50.985 --> 00:08:52.975
a groyse, hitung.

00:08:52.943 --> 00:08:54.540
un ver zaynen geven di hiter?

00:08:54.589 --> 00:08:55.627
di daytshn.

00:08:55.634 --> 00:08:57.083
di- dos zaynen geven daytshn?

00:08:57.151 --> 00:08:59.860
ye, mit di, mit di AVTOMATn.

00:08:59.902 --> 00:09:01.364
un zey hobn geredt daytsh, di vakh?

00:09:01.293 --> 00:09:02.607
ye. ye.

00:09:02.294 --> 00:09:03.865
di MALKEN-vakh hot geredt daytsh.

00:09:03.664 --> 00:09:05.131
ye, ye, ye.

00:09:04.655 --> 00:09:06.557
dos iz geven S.S., efsher veyst ir, neyn?

00:09:06.557 --> 00:09:07.434
S.S.

00:09:07.434 --> 00:09:08.799
 S.S.-vakh, ye?

00:09:08.799 --> 00:09:09.688
ye.

00:09:09.688 --> 00:09:12.452
un ver flegt aykh firn oyf der arbet? ver flegt aykh bagleytn?

00:09:12.452 --> 00:09:16.031
bagleytn iz oykh di S.S. merstn teyl.

00:09:16.031 --> 00:09:19.837
efsher gedenkt ir fun lager bizn arbets-ort

00:09:19.837 --> 00:09:22.908
fun MALKEN, hot ir gedarft lang geyn?

00:09:22.908 --> 00:09:24.030
lang.

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:25.188
vifl umgefer tsayt?

00:09:25.188 --> 00:09:28.855
nu? mistomen a

00:09:28.855 --> 00:09:30.995
a sho, onderhalbn.

00:09:30.995 --> 00:09:33.451
oybe nit mer; ver UNK flegt dos kukn?

00:09:33.451 --> 00:09:37.388
zey flegn undz firn un firn, firn un firn.

00:09:37.388 --> 00:09:43.399
tsum ende flegn zey undz firn un firn un firn, vi (undz), vu es hobn zikh dernentert di rusn flegn zey undz alts

00:09:43.399 --> 00:09:47.166
firn vayter un vayter un vayter un vayter un vayter.

00:09:46.134 --> 00:09:50.238
yo, ober i-, az ir flegt in MALKE- fun MALKEN geyn grobn di shuts...

00:09:49.188 --> 00:09:54.609
nu fun MALKE- fun Malkener lager az s'iz shoyn, s'hobn zikh shoyn dernentert di rusn

00:09:54.609 --> 00:09:58.925
flegn zey undz firn un firn efsher akhtsik hundert kilometer a tog.

00:09:58.925 --> 00:10:01.238
ah, dos ho- hot men aykh aroysgetribn fun lager.

00:10:01.013 --> 00:10:01.767
ye.

00:10:01.767 --> 00:10:03.547
dos hot men aykh evakuirt fun lager.

00:10:03.258 --> 00:10:07.539
evakuirt fun lager un zey flegn undz firn un firn un firn un firn.

00:10:07.539 --> 00:10:11.767
on a sof un on a breg. ikh gedenk azoy vi haynt; ikh fleg shoyn keyn koyekh nit hobn tsu geyn.

00:10:11.767 --> 00:10:14.925
flegt mir nemen vey ton der UNK fun veytog.

00:10:14.925 --> 00:10:18.644
un dernokh bay nakht flegn zey undz araynlozn vu nit iz in a saray.

00:10:18.644 --> 00:10:19.328
in a shayer?

00:10:19.328 --> 00:10:22.819
in a, nu, in a shtal aza min, un dortn flegt men nekhtikn.

00:10:21.043 --> 00:10:21.784
shtal?

00:10:22.819 --> 00:10:25.135
ah, un ir, lemoshl

00:10:25.135 --> 00:10:27.942
az ir flegt g- geyn grobn di shuts-griber, ye?

00:10:27.942 --> 00:10:28.188
ye.

00:10:28.188 --> 00:10:31.995
ir, ir flegt dos ton mit, ir hot aleyn gearbet mit a lopete?

00:10:34.889 --> 00:10:39.310
zogt az s'iz keyner nito.

00:10:39.310 --> 00:10:41.503
ir hot aleyn gearbet mit a lopete?

00:10:41.503 --> 00:10:42.153
ah?

00:10:42.153 --> 00:10:44.223
ir, ir flegt aleyn grobn mit a lopete?

00:10:44.223 --> 00:10:45.240
ya.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:47.333
aleyn grobn (onnemen) grobn, yo?

00:10:46.837 --> 00:10:47.837
ya, ya.

00:10:47.837 --> 00:10:50.486
un d- un di erd iz dan geven nit farfrorn?

00:10:50.486 --> 00:10:53.275
neyn, s'iz geven nit farfrorn.

00:10:53.275 --> 00:10:55.696
me fleg arbetn in di OKOPes.

00:10:55.696 --> 00:10:59.556
ir hot oysgeshlosn dem telefon? zeyer vikhtik, zeyer gut geton.

00:10:59.556 --> 00:11:01.784
 yo, dos vet undz itster nit shtern.

00:11:01.784 --> 00:11:02.608
nu, (DAVAI).

00:11:02.608 --> 00:11:03.696
un

00:11:03.696 --> 00:11:07.328
vu iz aykh, a bisl laykhter geven, tsu in STUTTHOF tsu in arbets-lager?

00:11:07.328 --> 00:11:11.187
oy, s'iz mir do geven shlekht un do geven shlekht.

00:11:11.187 --> 00:11:14.959
ir hot nisht gehat keyn kharote, kharote az ir hot farlozn dem S- STUTTHOF?

00:11:14.959 --> 00:11:20.030
neyn. kh'hob zikh gefreyt az ikh bin avekgeforn fun dortn, vayl ikh hob gezen az s'iz a SMERTEL'NYY lager.

00:11:20.030 --> 00:11:22.240
az s'iz a toyt-gefar, ye?

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:24.285
un in ale, un a-

00:11:23.591 --> 00:11:27.904
in do- dortn in lager iz oykh geven a gefar, iz oykh geven a toyt-gefar.

00:11:27.749 --> 00:11:28.942
in STUTTHOF, ye?

00:11:27.916 --> 00:11:30.713
ober, ye, ober in, lager.

00:11:30.713 --> 00:11:34.363
ober in lager shoyn nit azoy. derfar vayle me fleg frirn oyf der arbet.

00:11:34.363 --> 00:11:36.942
a mentsh vos arbet, tut men im keyn zakh nit.

00:11:36.942 --> 00:11:40.661
bay di daytshn iz oykh azoy geven. oyb m'iz geven krank, (hot men) nit gekent

00:11:40.661 --> 00:11:42.747
flegn zey nor zukhn (tsu UNICHTOZHenen).

00:11:42.747 --> 00:11:44.023
tsu farnikhtn, ye?

00:11:43.315 --> 00:11:45.345
nu yo, un az m'hot gearbet

00:11:45.345 --> 00:11:49.292
iz, heyst es az du bist nokh vert vos nit iz.

00:11:49.292 --> 00:11:53.473
(un di) zaynen geblibn lebn; az nit volt men dokh nit geblibn lebn.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:50.300
ah, iz

00:11:53.661 --> 00:11:57.415
iz, iz az di, di, di front hot zikh dernentert tsu aykh?

00:11:57.415 --> 00:12:02.626
vi- fu- vi s'hot dernentert der front, v- vu, vu nor di rusn flegn kumen on

00:12:02.626 --> 00:12:07.029
dortn flegn zey undz firn alts vayter un vayter un vayter un vayter.

00:12:07.029 --> 00:12:09.626
zey hobn undz gehat avekgefirt shoyn biz Berlin.

00:12:09.626 --> 00:12:10.685
kimat biz Berlin?

00:12:10.703 --> 00:12:11.400
ya.

00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:12.222
ale

00:12:12.222 --> 00:12:18.222
ale shtetlekh in Daytshland bin ikh oysgegangen, ober fregt mir in velkhn ikh bin geven gedenk ikh nit.

00:12:18.222 --> 00:12:22.976
dos gedenk ikh nit. ikh gedenk nor di bafrayung bin ikh geven in Poyln aleyn.

00:12:22.976 --> 00:12:25.292
in dos, in

00:12:25.292 --> 00:12:28.803
ir hot gezogt az ir flegt rizikirn un (afrier) loyfn; vu iz dos?

00:12:28.713 --> 00:12:31.555
dos iz geven shoyn ot zayendik

00:12:31.555 --> 00:12:34.485
zayendik vi zey flegn undz firn

00:12:34.485 --> 00:12:41.309
biz zey flegn undz firn vayter un vayter, un yeder tog flegt men zikh opshteln andersh(vu) vu nit iz

00:12:41.309 --> 00:12:43.833
f- hob ikh bashlosn az ikh darf

00:12:43.833 --> 00:12:48.590
aroysgeyn fun lager un zukhn vos nit iz (op tsum esn) vayl az nit vel ikh nit, dos nit aribertrogn.

00:12:48.590 --> 00:12:50.204
dos iz shoyn geven nit in MALKEN?

00:12:50.204 --> 00:12:51.186
neyn.

00:12:51.186 --> 00:12:52.190
dos iz shoyn geven

00:12:51.713 --> 00:12:54.411
dos iz shoyn geven az zey un-, flegn undz firn unter der vegns.

00:12:54.411 --> 00:12:55.785
unter der vegns, ye?

00:12:55.274 --> 00:12:57.888
un ikh fleg antloyfn un kumen dernokh oyf karik.

00:12:57.888 --> 00:12:59.424
vu, vu flegt ir loyfn?

00:12:59.424 --> 00:13:01.999
du- vu s'iz dort do a shtibl, a shtub.

00:13:01.999 --> 00:13:04.327
dos iz, gants oft flegt ir ton azelkhene zakhn?

00:13:04.327 --> 00:13:05.677
kimat yedn tog.

00:13:05.677 --> 00:13:06.555
yedn opshtel.

00:13:06.555 --> 00:13:07.379
ya.

00:13:07.379 --> 00:13:09.502
iz, vu, vu zayt ir gegangen?

00:13:09.502 --> 00:13:15.151
vu fleg ikh geyn? avu ikh fleg zen a shtibl, un dernokh fleg ikh zikh ayntseykhenen az ikh zol kenen kumen tsurik in lager.

00:13:15.151 --> 00:13:16.809
ir zol zikh nit farblondzhenen.

00:13:16.379 --> 00:13:17.256
nu, ye.

00:13:17.256 --> 00:13:20.520
 vos, ir flegt arayngeyn lemoshl in a shtibl, ye?

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:21.151
ye.

00:13:21.151 --> 00:13:22.116
vos flegt ir zogn?

00:13:22.116 --> 00:13:26.063
mm, keyn zakh fleg ikh nit zogn, zey flegn dokh shoyn zen undzer oyszen mit di du-

00:13:26.063 --> 00:13:30.888
di daytshn flegn nit araynlozn; di daytshn flegn shrayen "LOS fun ir, LOS fun ir."

00:13:30.888 --> 00:13:36.168
zey flegn moyre hobn; zaynen nit geven azoy shlekht, vi zey flegn moyre hobn me zol zey nit shisn.

00:13:36.168 --> 00:13:40.081
un di polyakn, di poyln, di polyakn flegn gebn esn.

00:13:40.081 --> 00:13:42.356
ikh fleg onheybn esn; zey flegn mir aleyn gebn.

00:13:42.063 --> 00:13:43.835
ah, ir hot gekent den redn poylish?

00:13:43.713 --> 00:13:44.853
a bisinke.

00:13:44.853 --> 00:13:47.397
ir, ir hot a bisl geredt vegn di polyakn, tsu keyn zakh nit?

00:13:47.397 --> 00:13:48.240
neyn.

00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:50.226
zey flegn poshet aykh gebn esn, un

00:13:49.770 --> 00:13:52.589
ikh fleg mit zey reydn oyf poylish.

00:13:52.589 --> 00:13:56.168
ikh fleg zey zogn, ikh ken a bisinke poylish.

00:13:56.168 --> 00:13:58.765
IA UMEIU NEMNOZHKO PO...

00:13:58.765 --> 00:14:02.730
PO POLSKOMU, zey flegn mir gebn.

00:14:02.730 --> 00:14:04.589
yo, un

00:14:04.589 --> 00:14:07.476
un ir flegt dortn opesn, tsu ir flegt nokh brengen aheym oykhet?

00:14:06.975 --> 00:14:12.186
ikh fleg opesn, un ikh flegn brengen in lager, fleg ikh brengen far mayn shviger, far mayn shvegerin.

00:14:12.186 --> 00:14:19.186
un ver es fleg zitsn a hungeriker fleg ikh alemen onkormenen, avekgebn dos vos ikh fleg farn tog flegt mir gebn.

00:14:19.186 --> 00:14:22.726
aha. un aykh iz ale mol gelungen zikh araynshmuglen (ahin)

00:14:22.115 --> 00:14:28.238
ah, ye, gelungen, ikh bin geven zeyer a, ikh bin geven zeyer MAGER; kh'hob gevegn draysik KILO.

00:14:28.238 --> 00:14:30.905
ikh fleg zayn zeyer a gre- a gikhe.

00:14:30.905 --> 00:14:34.835
in di minutn fleg ikh arayngeyn; in di minutn fleg ikh aroysgeyn, un VSE.

00:14:34.835 --> 00:14:38.956
ah, vayle dan, dan hot ir shoyn nit gehat, a tsam; ir zayt shoyn nit geven fartsamt.

00:14:38.297 --> 00:14:40.378
neyn, neyn.

00:14:40.378 --> 00:14:44.619
ikh bin eyn mol, hot zikh ongetshepet on mir eyne a froy, a lererke iz zi geven, Leye

00:14:44.010 --> 00:14:44.782
a yidishe?

00:14:44.782 --> 00:14:46.583
a yidishe. Leye hot men ir gerufn.

00:14:46.203 --> 00:14:47.343
fun vanet iz zi geven?

00:14:47.343 --> 00:14:49.361
a Kovner.

00:14:49.361 --> 00:14:53.527
ikh hob ir nit gekent azoy, hot zi zikh ongetshepet ikh zol ir mitnemen tsu geyn mit ir.

00:14:53.527 --> 00:14:57.797
tsuza- mit mir tsuzamen; zi vil oykh aroysgeyn (zukhn) vos nit iz tsum esn.

00:14:57.659 --> 00:14:58.881
betn shpayz, ye?

00:14:58.548 --> 00:14:59.959
ye.

00:14:59.959 --> 00:15:03.378
vi mir zaynen aroys, ikh bin gegangen mit ir.

00:15:03.378 --> 00:15:07.378
ikh her me shrayt "HALT, HALT!"

00:15:07.378 --> 00:15:11.255
"oy," zog ikh, "Leyinke, ir zayt mir nit geven mazldik!

00:15:11.255 --> 00:15:14.045
az ikh gey aleyn flegt mir keyner nit bamerkn.

00:15:14.045 --> 00:15:17.448
un do gey ikh, s'iz zalbe tsveyt un s'iz tsvey lates!"

00:15:17.448 --> 00:15:20.975
zog ikh "do iz shoyn undzer ende; do shist men undz op."

00:15:20.975 --> 00:15:24.536
un me shrayt "HALT, HALT" un mir geyen. mir makhn zikh nit herndik.

00:15:24.536 --> 00:15:26.641
mit a mol zog ikh

00:15:26.641 --> 00:15:31.009
"veyst ir vos? me darf zikh opshteln; vi s'vet zayn vet zayn.

00:15:31.009 --> 00:15:35.290
oybe s'iz bashert der toyt, iz vet men undz shisn, nu vos ken do zayn?

00:15:35.290 --> 00:15:38.080
azoy un azoy iz shoyn der toyt."

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:39.816
zogt zi:

00:15:39.816 --> 00:15:45.922
zog ikh, "ir zayt a lererke, kent ir beser reydn fun mir daytsh; tomer (me vet) UNK fregn vos, zolt ir zey entfern.

00:15:45.922 --> 00:15:50.378
vayle mir" zog ikh, "varft vi kadokhes; ikh ken nit reydn!"

00:15:50.378 --> 00:15:52.992
meyle, er zogt nokh a mol "HALT!

00:15:52.992 --> 00:15:55.781
un oyb ir vet zikh nit opshteln," zogt er, "vel ikh aykh shisn."

00:15:55.781 --> 00:15:57.214
dos iz, oyf daytsh iz dos geven.

00:15:57.009 --> 00:15:58.132
ya.

00:15:58.132 --> 00:16:04.009
meyle, mir hobn zikh opgeshtelt. mir hobn zikh opgeshtelt, un, un er iz tsu, a hoykher, a feldfebl

00:16:04.009 --> 00:16:08.957
a sheyner, a krasavets, iz zayn ponem zikh nit ayntsukukn fun sheynkeyt.

00:16:08.957 --> 00:16:11.150
zogt er "vu geyt ir?

00:16:11.150 --> 00:16:17.921
"vu geyt ir? ver zayt ir azelkhene? mit lates oyfn rukn" zogt er, "ikh hob glaykh gezen az ir zayt heftlinger."

00:16:17.921 --> 00:16:19.746
nu, hobn mir im gezogt.

00:16:19.746 --> 00:16:23.255
gezogt dem emes, azoy vi mir hobn zikh farlorn fun lager.

00:16:23.255 --> 00:16:25.360
mir hobn nit gezogt az mir zaynen antlofn.

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.781
mir hobn zikh farlorn.

00:16:27.781 --> 00:16:31.834
zogt er "to vi azoy hot ir zikh farlorn?" nu, zog ikh, zogt zi "mir hobn zikh farlorn.

00:16:31.834 --> 00:16:35.588
mir zaynen gegangen farklert un mir hobn zikh farlorn."

00:16:35.588 --> 00:16:39.307
meyle, zogt er, "nu, to gut. kumt mit mir."

00:16:39.307 --> 00:16:42.219
gey ikh mit ir, un ikh zog tsu ir:

00:16:42.219 --> 00:16:44.184
"nu, do iz shoyn undzer ende.

00:16:44.184 --> 00:16:48.149
"do iz shoyn undzer ende; (er iz aroyf) un zi iz undzer ende."

00:16:48.149 --> 00:16:52.447
nu zogt zi, "meyle, s'iz alts farfaln, ikh bin aykh geven nit mazldik, un azoy iz bashert.

00:16:52.447 --> 00:16:55.658
un mir geyen beyde, mir hobn shoyn eyne tsum andern keyn taynes nit!

00:16:55.658 --> 00:16:57.658
vi s'vet zayn, azoy s'vet zayn!"

00:16:57.658 --> 00:17:01.377
meyle, er hot undz gebrakht tsu firn, er hot undz gebrakht tsu firn.

00:17:01.377 --> 00:17:05.237
arayngefirt in a kirkh, zaynen gezesn soldatn.

00:17:05.237 --> 00:17:08.237
ful, daytshn, geshlofn oyf der erd.

00:17:08.237 --> 00:17:13.307
"oy" zog ikh, "vey iz mir. vos firt er undzer? vu firt er undzer? oy vey, mayne yorn" zog ikh.

00:17:13.307 --> 00:17:18.710
"a klog tsu mayne yorn. UNK vos UNK (zol ikh do) batrakhtn zog ikh mit di soldatn mit di (dos)."

00:17:18.710 --> 00:17:21.237
un zi shoyn aleyn tsitert shoyn oykh.

00:17:21.237 --> 00:17:24.745
meyle, er zogt tsu undz. "HUNGER HABEN SIE?"

00:17:24.745 --> 00:17:25.938
zogn mir "ye."

00:17:25.938 --> 00:17:27.304
dos heyst, tsu ir zayt hungerik.

00:17:27.096 --> 00:17:29.069
ye. "HABEN SIE HUNGER?"

00:17:29.069 --> 00:17:30.999
zogn mir "JA, JA."

00:17:30.999 --> 00:17:34.578
nu zogt er, "to vart. ikh'l aykh brengen vos tsum esn."

00:17:34.578 --> 00:17:37.596
meyle er iz avek; hot dos gedoyert

00:17:37.596 --> 00:17:43.350
un er hot undz gebrakht tsu trogn, latkes gebakene mit ko- mit KOFE

00:17:43.350 --> 00:17:48.192
nu, zog ikh "oyb er git undz latkes mit KOFE, vet er undz dem toyt nit makhn mistame."

00:17:48.192 --> 00:17:50.297
ikh zog dos tsu ir.

00:17:50.297 --> 00:17:56.104
nu, un er hot undz avekgezetst, geheysn zikh zetsn bay a tish un esn; zogn mir "mir veln zikh nit zetsn.

00:17:56.104 --> 00:18:01.543
derfar" zogn mir "vayle mir hobn layz a sakh. mir veln dir onts- ontrogn di layz."

00:18:01.543 --> 00:18:03.981
oy, er hot zikh dershrokn vi er derhert di layz.

00:18:03.981 --> 00:18:06.174
zogt er "far vos hot ir nit gezogt?"

00:18:06.174 --> 00:18:08.209
hot er undz glaykh avekgefirt

00:18:08.209 --> 00:18:13.932
in a, in a, aroysgefirt oyf a hoyf, un arayngefirt in aza min SANDELIUKAS, un gege-

00:18:13.245 --> 00:18:14.560
UNK vos iz a SANDELIUKAS

00:18:14.560 --> 00:18:16.166
nu, a s-, a

00:18:15.771 --> 00:18:16.473
a shpaykhler?

00:18:16.473 --> 00:18:17.385
a sht-

00:18:17.385 --> 00:18:18.075
a shtibl.

00:18:17.911 --> 00:18:18.771
a SKLADIK.

00:18:18.771 --> 00:18:19.881
a shtibl aza.

00:18:19.490 --> 00:18:25.648
ye, un er hot undz glaykh gegebn vos zikh ontsuton andere, un alts hot er undz geheysn oyston un avekvarfn di layz.

00:18:25.648 --> 00:18:29.525
hobn mir azoy geton, un dernokh hot er undz gebrakht tsu firn

00:18:29.525 --> 00:18:32.490
un er hot undz gegebn opesn

00:18:32.490 --> 00:18:34.981
un dernokh hot er undz gegebn opesn

00:18:34.981 --> 00:18:38.946
un nokhn opesn zogt er "kumt mit mir."

00:18:38.946 --> 00:18:43.666
un er hot undz ongeleygt tashes ful mit esn.

00:18:43.666 --> 00:18:50.139
az mir hobn nit gehat avu tsu nemen; mir hobn gekukt eyne oyf di andere; mir hobn dos nit vi tsu nemen, un mir hobn dos nit keyn koyekh tsu trogn.

00:18:50.139 --> 00:18:52.101
afile a varenye azelkhene

00:18:51.858 --> 00:18:53.178
ayngemakhts, ya?

00:18:52.525 --> 00:18:53.669
ye.

00:18:53.669 --> 00:18:58.069
un er hot undz altsding opgegebn, un er zogt "geyt, un gefint dem lager.

00:18:58.069 --> 00:19:01.858
vayl oyb ir vet nit gefinen dem lager, iz vu vel ikh aykh ahinton?"

00:19:01.858 --> 00:19:05.012
zogn mir "mir veln gefinen, BESPOKOIet zikh UNK."

00:19:04.244 --> 00:19:05.628
um- baumruik zikh nit.

00:19:05.367 --> 00:19:07.297
ye, mir veln gefinen.

00:19:07.297 --> 00:19:09.490
meyle, mir geyen shoyn beyde tsufridene.

00:19:09.490 --> 00:19:10.560
un er geyt nokh aykh?

00:19:10.560 --> 00:19:12.215
neyn. er hot undz geheysn geyn.

00:19:12.215 --> 00:19:13.750
aleyn, on a vakh, on ba-

00:19:13.228 --> 00:19:16.309
on a va-, on a vakh, on keyn zakh, un er hot undz onge-

00:19:15.086 --> 00:19:16.297
nor mit, mit a s-

00:19:16.309 --> 00:19:18.507
ongezogt az mir zoln nor nit far- far-

00:19:18.506 --> 00:19:19.342
farblondzhen.

00:19:19.174 --> 00:19:22.665
farblondzhen. un mir zaynen avek, iz shoyn gegangen der lager.

00:19:22.665 --> 00:19:26.542
er hot undz a tsay- a tsayt farhaltn, mir hobn shoyn gekent farzamen dem lager.

00:19:26.542 --> 00:19:30.542
un mir zaynen arayn tsvishn lagern, VSE, un avek, mit di produktn.

00:19:30.542 --> 00:19:34.062
ye, u- aykh iz geven dan shver tsu geyn, vayl ir hot gehat a

00:19:32.525 --> 00:19:34.332
nu, farshteyt zikh!

00:19:34.332 --> 00:19:40.333
ober, dernokh zaynen mir gekumen in a SKLADIK un mir hobn zikh funandergeteylt; ale mir hobn dos oyfgegesn.

00:19:40.333 --> 00:19:42.982
un mir hobn gedankt got az me hot undz nit opgeshosn.

00:19:42.982 --> 00:19:45.684
iz daf- dafke iz dos geven a mazldiker tog.

00:19:45.508 --> 00:19:46.578
ya!

00:19:46.578 --> 00:19:47.367
so-

00:19:46.681 --> 00:19:48.438
dos iz geven a mazldiker tog.

00:19:47.841 --> 00:19:49.821
sof-kol-sof hot zikh aroysgevizn

00:19:48.753 --> 00:19:51.209
ye, ye, s'iz geven a mazldiker.

00:19:51.209 --> 00:19:53.525
d- er iz vayzt oys geven nit keyn daytsh.

00:19:53.525 --> 00:19:56.122
er hot gemuzt zayn a komunist, oder ver

00:19:56.122 --> 00:20:00.315
vayl az nit (ven er) volt geven a daytsh, volt er zikh mit undz andersh bagangen.

00:20:00.315 --> 00:20:02.876
er iz vayzt oys nit- oy vi sheyn er iz geven.

