er hot undz arayngefirt epes alts bazunder, bazunder, un alts gegebn.

00:20:20.542 --> 00:20:25.214
 un and- un vi er hot aykh aroysge- bagleyt hot keyner fun andere daytshn nisht gezen?

00:20:24.680 --> 00:20:26.577
neyn. neyn.

