un oyb ir vet farshpetikn dem lager zolt ir kumen tsu mir, vel ikh zen vos tsu ton mit aykh."

00:20:36.612 --> 00:20:41.068
(kh'trakht mir) s'iz okh un vey vos vet zayn UNK darfn tun, ton mit undz.

00:20:41.068 --> 00:20:42.647
fa-, ober fayn fun im!

00:20:42.647 --> 00:20:43.560
yo, zeyer sheyn.

00:20:43.560 --> 00:20:47.770
un, un nokh dem i- zayt ir, un dos iz geven der eyntsiker mol

00:20:47.770 --> 00:20:50.858
vi, vi aykh hot men azoy geholfn in tsayt fun der milkhome?

00:20:50.858 --> 00:20:52.384
dos iz der eyntsiker mol.

00:20:52.384 --> 00:20:54.547
ven a, a daytsh zol aykh azoy helfn, yo?

00:20:54.104 --> 00:20:57.521
v- ver veys ver er i-, az er iz nit geven keyn daytsh. neyn.

00:20:56.788 --> 00:20:58.507
ober er hot dokh geredt daytsh.

00:20:58.507 --> 00:21:01.560
er hot ge- s'iz nit vikhtik; er ken reydn daytsh.

00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:06.122
un efsher iz er geven a daytsh. ver veys? ver veys?

00:21:06.369 --> 00:21:08.753
nor mir hobn gehat tsurik dem tog.

00:21:08.753 --> 00:21:11.595
nu, s'hot undz geklekt.

00:21:11.595 --> 00:21:15.762
un, dernokh, z- flegt ir, zayt ir vayter gegangen, un gegangen biz

00:21:15.174 --> 00:21:17.622
gegangen biz di letste minut. az nit

00:21:16.982 --> 00:21:17.386
ir

00:21:17.622 --> 00:21:19.297
az nit volt ikh nit geblibn lebn.

00:21:19.297 --> 00:21:21.805
der marsh, hot gedoyert a sakh tsayt?

00:21:21.805 --> 00:21:22.785
velkhe marsh?

00:21:22.613 --> 00:21:25.595
nu, vos me fleg (geyn) tsu tog tsu tog firn un firn un firn?

00:21:25.595 --> 00:21:27.139
oy, s'hot gedoyert!

00:21:27.139 --> 00:21:31.086
vu di day- vu di rusn flegn zikh dernentern dortn flegn zey undz (alts) avekfirn.

00:21:31.086 --> 00:21:34.560
zey hobn undz shoyn gehat avekgefirt biz Berlin, nor in Berlin bin ikh shoyn nit geven.

00:21:34.560 --> 00:21:37.384
mir hobn zikh shoyn gehat bafrayt in Khino(v).

00:21:37.384 --> 00:21:38.683
vu hot men aykh bafrayt?

00:21:38.683 --> 00:21:39.577
in Khino(v).

00:21:39.577 --> 00:21:40.472
in Khinov?

00:21:41.034 --> 00:21:43.220
ir gedenkt dem tog vi hot men ay-

00:21:42.647 --> 00:21:43.911
dem tsentn MART.

00:21:43.911 --> 00:21:45.858
i- dem tog gedenkt ir?

00:21:45.858 --> 00:21:48.250
dem tog gedenk ikh nit, nor dem tsentn MART

00:21:47.560 --> 00:21:49.654
neyn, ober vos hot pasirt in dem tog?

00:21:49.454 --> 00:21:54.139
nu dem tog iz, di, di vakh iz farfaln gevorn efsher.

00:21:54.139 --> 00:21:57.244
ir zayt dan geven in a, in a tsaytvaylikn lager, ye?

00:21:57.244 --> 00:21:58.858
nit in keyn lager.

00:21:58.858 --> 00:22:00.345
vu zayt ir geven d-

00:21:59.700 --> 00:22:02.226
zaynen mir shoyn geven in, in, in sarayen.

00:22:02.226 --> 00:22:03.631
in a, in a, in a shayter.

00:22:03.489 --> 00:22:04.016
ye.

00:22:04.016 --> 00:22:05.261
in a shayer.

00:22:05.261 --> 00:22:07.805
un, un, un in der fri?

00:22:07.805 --> 00:22:09.559
in der fri oykh in shayer.

00:22:09.405 --> 00:22:11.825
un ir hot, un vos, ir hot dershpirt az s'iz nito keyn vakh?

00:22:11.647 --> 00:22:13.103
az s'iz nito di vakh.

00:22:13.103 --> 00:22:15.980
kh'vel dokh aykh shoyn nit hobn vos tsu dertseyln in di andere kasete.

00:22:15.980 --> 00:22:18.059
nit vikhtik, dertseylt vos iz geven.

00:22:17.103 --> 00:22:20.033
nu, nu ot o VOT, UNK (efsher).

00:22:20.033 --> 00:22:25.314
undz aroysge- aroysge(UNK), hob ikh gezen az di vakh iz nito; zog ikh "me darf shoyn geyn fun danet."

00:22:25.314 --> 00:22:28.595
a sakh froyen zayt ir geven in, in yenem sha- shayer?

00:22:28.244 --> 00:22:29.875
a sakh.

00:22:29.875 --> 00:22:32.097
me flegt oysshtarbn ey-, mir flegn

00:22:32.097 --> 00:22:36.191
ot flegt men shlofn un ot flegt men shtarbn, eyne lebn di andere.

00:22:36.191 --> 00:22:40.015
V OBSHCHEM iz gekle- s'hot geklekt. s'hot geklekt.

00:22:40.015 --> 00:22:43.314
un, ah, az ir hot dershpirt az di vakh iz shoyn nito.

00:22:43.314 --> 00:22:45.875
bin ikh, hob ikh zikh ongeton un ikh bin gegangen.

00:22:45.875 --> 00:22:47.068
a- aleyn oyf

00:22:47.068 --> 00:22:48.156
ye, aleyn.

00:22:48.156 --> 00:22:49.524
un v- vu zayt ir avek?

00:22:49.524 --> 00:22:50.577
in shtetl.

00:22:50.577 --> 00:22:52.198
vos far a shtetl iz dortn geven?

00:22:52.103 --> 00:22:54.331
veys ikh nit vi azoy zi hot zikh gerufn.

00:22:54.331 --> 00:22:57.226
fun Khinov fun d-, fun dem saray bin ikh avek

00:22:57.226 --> 00:23:03.892
un ikh ze fun vaytn vi s'forn shoyn rusn; zey shrayen "TOVARISHCHI, VY SVOBODNY, VY KHODITE OTSIUDA, VY SVOBODNY!"

00:23:03.892 --> 00:23:07.805
"NE BOITES', NIKTO VAS NE TRONET, TEPER' VAS NIKTO NE TRONET"

00:23:07.805 --> 00:23:09.243
ir hot dan farshtanen rusish?

00:23:09.243 --> 00:23:10.226
ya!

00:23:10.226 --> 00:23:11.523
ir hot gekent rusish?

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:12.612
ya!

00:23:12.612 --> 00:23:14.124
fun vanet hot ir gekent rusi-?

00:23:13.647 --> 00:23:18.419
far vos zol ikh nit kenen? ikh hob gelebt dokh, ikh hob dokh gelebt in Lite.

00:23:18.419 --> 00:23:18.998
un

00:23:18.998 --> 00:23:21.664
ober ikh, fleg ikh kenen reydn a mol, flegn zayn rusn.

00:23:21.664 --> 00:23:24.166
ah, fun d- ayere shkheynim hot ir zikh oysgelernt.

00:23:23.646 --> 00:23:25.173
nu, KONECHNO.

00:23:25.173 --> 00:23:28.822
ah, ot, zayt ir, az di rusn hobn genumen shrayen az ir zayt fray

00:23:28.678 --> 00:23:33.682
ye. "TOVARISHCHI, VY SVOBODNY, VY KHODITE, NIKTO VAS NE TRONET" zey hobn

00:23:33.682 --> 00:23:39.068
zey hobn gevorfn broyt, konservn, zey hobn gevorfn tsum esn, "nemt, est!

00:23:39.068 --> 00:23:43.161
VY SVOBODNY, VY SVOBODNY, VY KHODITE, VY KHODITE"

00:23:42.677 --> 00:23:44.571
ober ir zayt shoyn aroys frier aleyn.

00:23:44.075 --> 00:23:45.692
ye.

00:23:45.692 --> 00:23:47.173
un vu zayt ir avek?

00:23:47.173 --> 00:23:48.260
in shtetl.

00:23:48.260 --> 00:23:51.488
 b- dos iz geven a poylishe shtetl tsu a daytshishe?

00:23:51.488 --> 00:23:54.190
(ver) dortn hobn gelebt i polyakn i daytshn.

00:23:54.190 --> 00:23:56.095
un ir zayt vayter avek betn, tsu nit?

00:23:56.015 --> 00:23:58.611
neyn. ikh bin shoyn betn nit gegangen.

00:23:58.611 --> 00:23:59.980
(az me darf nit) shoyn betn

00:23:59.980 --> 00:24:03.453
az s'iz shoyn alts geven fray; ikh bin arayn in a shtub

00:24:03.453 --> 00:24:08.453
hob ikh zeyer gevelt esn, bin ikh arayn in a shtub vos s'iz dortn geven fun alts tsum esn.

00:24:08.453 --> 00:24:11.845
un ikh hob m- gehat moyre tomer iz dortn opgesamt

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:12.750
ah, di shtub iz geven a leydike.

00:24:12.611 --> 00:24:16.541
a leydike, hob ikh genumen a kats, kh'hob ir gegebn frier di kats esn.

00:24:16.541 --> 00:24:22.155
trakht ikh "oybe di kats vet esn un zi vet nit aniderfaln ken men esn, un oybe nit ken men dos nit esn."

00:24:22.155 --> 00:24:26.909
hot zi opgegesn, ikh hob opgevart a vayle un zi falt nit. zi lebt, zi geyt zukhn nokh.

00:24:26.909 --> 00:24:31.137
hob ikh shoyn aleyn genumen esn; hob ikh zikh ongegesn, un ikh bin krank gevorn.

00:24:31.137 --> 00:24:33.962
o- oyf v- oyf vos zayt ir gevorn krank?

00:24:33.962 --> 00:24:39.874
ver veys oyf vos? mir hot genumen vey ton der mogn mit mayn gantser kerper.

00:24:39.874 --> 00:24:40.646
ye.

00:24:40.646 --> 00:24:43.172
un vos iz mit aykh far(UNK)? vos iz pasirt mit aykh?

00:24:43.172 --> 00:24:45.881
nu dernokh bin ikh gegangen vayter.

00:24:45.365 --> 00:24:46.260
a kranke?

00:24:46.260 --> 00:24:51.751
ya, hob ikh getrofn shoyn mayn shviger mit mayn shvegerin, hob ikh zikh avekgezetst oyfn mitn gas.

00:24:51.751 --> 00:24:56.628
un ikh zog "mer gey ikh fun danet a trit nit vayl ikh ken nit geyn, ikh bin zeyer krank."

00:24:56.628 --> 00:25:01.839
"ikh muz zikh vu nit iz geyn avekleygn. ikh muz lign, ikh bin zeyer krank."

00:25:01.839 --> 00:25:06.224
meyle, zey hobn mir koym tsu ge- koym hobn zey mir derfirt biz a sh-

00:25:06.224 --> 00:25:10.716
a shtub aza min iz geven. UNK daytshn hobn, a daytshke dortn geven.

00:25:10.716 --> 00:25:14.347
hobn mir ongeklapt, iz aroys a hoykhe, a grobe.

00:25:14.347 --> 00:25:18.663
hobn mir ir gebetn zi zol mir lozn zikh avekleygn vu nit iz, khotsh oyf a

00:25:18.663 --> 00:25:24.982
oyf a, in a vinkele, zogt zi "neyn, LOS fun HIER UNK." zi lozt nit.

00:25:24.982 --> 00:25:27.771
in dem minut iz untergekumen a rus.

