vos iz dos oyf yidish, vos hot er gezogt oyf rusish, vos batayt dos oyf yidish?

00:25:44.964 --> 00:25:48.473
oyf yidish? "oy, ikh bin" zog ikh "fun lager."

00:25:48.473 --> 00:25:54.666
"ikh bin" zog ikh "ah, ah, ikh bin UNK azoy krank gevorn" zog ikh. "kh'hob zikh ongegesn tsu fil un ikh bin zeyer krank.

00:25:54.666 --> 00:25:56.894
ikh ken" zog ikh "a trit nit shteln."

00:25:56.894 --> 00:26:02.736
zogt er "hob nit keyn fardrus. bald veln mir dir makhn alts in ordenung. mir veln dir avekleygn un brengen a dokter

00:26:02.736 --> 00:26:05.402
un alts vos m'vet darfn." klapt er on bay di day-

00:26:05.402 --> 00:26:10.297
klapt er on bay di daytshke un er zogt ir az zi zol zikh mir lozn avekleygn, zogt zi zi lozt nit.

00:26:10.297 --> 00:26:14.521
zogt er "AKH TY," ir veyst dokh mit a (MATUSHKE), zogt er

00:26:13.753 --> 00:26:15.486
ye, mit a zidlvort.

00:26:15.350 --> 00:26:16.069
ye.

00:26:16.069 --> 00:26:20.192
"du meynst" zogt er "az dos iz Hitler nokh do?

00:26:20.192 --> 00:26:25.578
vos" zogt er "lo- vos" zogt er "lozst (ir) zikh UNK afile nit avekleygn az zi iz a oysgemutshete a kranke?

00:26:25.578 --> 00:26:29.893
Hitler" zogt (tsu ir) zogt er az (er) iz shoyn KAPUT; er vet oyf tsurik nit kumen."

00:26:29.893 --> 00:26:34.209
meyle, zi hot nit gevelt lozn, hot er ir ongenumen un gegebn a gutn brik in

00:26:34.209 --> 00:26:36.016
hintn un er hot ir aroysgevorfn.

00:26:36.016 --> 00:26:36.944
fun, fun ir shtub?

00:26:36.876 --> 00:26:40.279
fun ir shtub, un hot undz arayn- mir arayngenumen, un m'hot

00:26:40.279 --> 00:26:46.174
un m'iz tsu tsum shafe un m'hot aroysgenumen vesh, mit alts, un ikh hob zikh anidergeleygt oyfn sofe.

00:26:46.174 --> 00:26:50.262
un dernokh iz er avek un gebrakht a dokter, un ikh bin dan opgelegn dray vokhn.

00:26:50.262 --> 00:26:51.612
in dem zelbikn shtibele?

