ver?

00:26:56.631 --> 00:27:00.262
di daytshke, az m'hot ir shoyn aroysgetribn un me lozt azoy nit

00:27:00.262 --> 00:27:03.928
un me lozt azoy nit geyn keyn zakh.

00:27:03.928 --> 00:27:09.754
iz, o- un ikh hob dokh a ha- veyst dokh a yidishe harts, zogn mir tsu im, tsum rus "loz ir arayn.

00:27:09.754 --> 00:27:14.140
brekht zi shoyn dem (shabn), loz ir arayn in eyn tsimer un zol zi zayn."

